Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上制服，还得收拾整齐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dress uniforms. Spit and polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道自己还能忍受多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know how much longer I'm going to be able to stand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛有人在掐我的脖子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I feel like my neck's in a sling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯代表是最后一批\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Vulcans are the last group of delegates we have to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们顺利上船，我们就轻松了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As soon as we get them aboard, we'll be able to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧，今天晚上还有个正式的接风晚宴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sure. A formal reception tonight, 114 delegates aboard for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这两周来陆续有114位代表登船，其中还有32位大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thirty-two of them ambassadors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们互相看不顺眼，像原始反物质堆一样敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Half of them mad at the other half, and the whole lot touchier
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,更何况这次还有柯林丹星的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than a raw antimatter pile over this Coridan question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,载有沙瑞克大使一行人的穿梭机准备进场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shuttlecraft approaching with Ambassador Sarek's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,预计抵达时间：1分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Estimate arrival: One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,允许着陆，契科夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bring them aboard, Mr. Chekov.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,穿梭机准备进港，礼宾队到机库甲板准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by to recover shuttlecraft. Honour guard to the Hangar Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,机库甲板准备就绪，机库甲板准备就绪，准备减压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Clear Hangar Deck. Clear Hangar Deck. Depressurising.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,接收穿梭机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Recovering shuttlecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,机库甲板减压完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hangar Deck pressurising.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人怎么打招呼来的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does that Vulcan salute go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这比穿制服还别扭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That hurts worse than the uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆士·寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain James Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大副，史波克中校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My first officer, Commander Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对于您的到来我们感到非常荣幸，很乐意为您效劳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcan honours us with your presence. We come to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 由您来接待令我们倍感荣幸，舰长 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Your service honours us, captain. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,首席医疗官，麦考伊医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chief Medical Officer Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大使 - 医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ambassador. - Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的副官，同时也是我的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My aides, and she who is my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的荣幸，女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our pleasure, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,等您安顿好，我会带您参观我们的舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As soon as you're settled, I'll arrange a tour of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克先生会作为您的向导 - 舰长，请换个人做向导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock will conduct you. - I prefer another guide, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如您所愿，大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you wish, ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我们会在两小时后离开瓦肯轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, we'll leave orbit in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要传送过去看你父母？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you care to beam down and visit your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克大使和他的妻子就是我的父母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ambassador Sarek and his wife are my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去发现新的世界和新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilisations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：茶包泰迪\N校对：喜马拉雅{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,第二季第十集\N「巴别塔之旅」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3842.3\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3842.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离开了瓦肯星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have departed Vulcan for the neutral planetoid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,启程前往代号为巴别塔的中立小行星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}code-named Babel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这个行星正好处于我们的星域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since it is in our sector, the Enterprise has been assigned
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号受命护送各联邦星系大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to transport ambassadors of Federation planets
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,前往参加这个重要的会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to this vitally important council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会议将讨论非常复杂的政治问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The issues of the council are politically complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,乘客之间气氛非常紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The passengers, explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是轮机室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the Engineering section.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有多台设备可以作为主控台的备用系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are a number of emergency back-up systems for the main controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那边是一组中控电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Over here are a number of control computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,跟人类相处这么多年，你始终没学会微笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After all these years among humans, you still haven't learned to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的微笑表达不了多少情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Humans smile with so little provocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有四年没回来看我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you haven't come to see us in four years, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲与我之间的关系并没有什么改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The situation between my father and myself has not changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人，请过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My wife, attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，可以请你过来一下吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock. A moment, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请解释一下计算机的组成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Explain the computer components.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，是我给史波克上的计算机启蒙教育\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gave Spock his first instruction in computers, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有用这些知识回报瓦肯星科学研究会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He chose to devote his knowledge to Starfleet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而是选择把它们奉献给星际舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}instead of the Vulcan Science Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you will excuse me, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生，很抱歉，我不是故意要冒犯你，我是想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, ambassador. I did not mean to offend. I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,冒犯是人类的情感，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Offence is a human emotion, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备返回我的休息室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm returning to my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请代我继续，夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continue, my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克夫人，我不太明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Sarek, I just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我阿曼达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你恐怕不会念我的瓦肯星名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm afraid you couldn't pronounce the Vulcan name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你能念出来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在练习多年后只能算是勉强会念了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, after a fashion and after many years of practise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能继续参观吗？我丈夫希望我能继续看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shall we continue the tour? My husband did request it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是听上去更像是个命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It sounded more like a command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的，他是瓦肯人，我是他的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course. He's a Vulcan. I'm his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克是他的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Spock is his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能理解，舰长，瓦肯人做事要遵从逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't understand the Vulcan way, captain. It's logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这比我们感情用事要好，但却并不容易做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a better way than ours. But it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克和沙瑞克已经有18年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has kept Spock and Sarek from speaking as father and son
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没像人类父子那样对话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for 18 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克是我最好的大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock is my best officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴他有你这样的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad he has such a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这对史波克来说非常不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It hasn't been easy on Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,既不是人类，也不是瓦肯星人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Neither human nor Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,除了星际舰队，他找不到其他的归属\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At home nowhere, except Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I take it that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是史波克在工作问题上违逆他父亲的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock disagreed with his father on the choice of career.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的丈夫并不反感星际舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My husband has nothing against Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是瓦肯人认为，和平不应该依靠武力来获得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Vulcans believe that peace should not depend on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,星际舰队只有迫不得已才使用武力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starfleet force is used only as a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也是文明社会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're an instrument of civilisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,星际舰队对于一个想要研究宇宙的科学家而言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it's a better opportunity for a scientist to study the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,确实比瓦肯星科学院要更生动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than he could get at the Vulcan Science Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沙瑞克希望史波克能够遵从他的教导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Sarek wanted Spock to follow his teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就像沙瑞克当年遵从他父亲教导一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as Sarek followed the teachings of his own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都很固执\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're both stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,人之本性，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A human trait, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥呼叫寇克舰长 - 不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bridge to Captain Kirk. - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我接收到一些信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I picked up some sort of signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一些符号，没有确切的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just a few symbols, nothing intelligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,来源？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Source?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我觉得诡异的，先生，没办法予以定位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what bothers me, sir. Impossible to locate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,接收到的信号量不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There wasn't enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,感应器在那一区域没有检测到任何物质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensors show nothing in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但信号很强烈，说明信号源离我们很近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it was a strong signal, as though it was very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,进入四级警戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go to Alert Status Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,启动远程扫描，完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Begin long-range scanning. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3842.4\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3842.4.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这次星际大会将会讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Interplanetary Conference will consider the petition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是否考虑接受柯林丹星加入联邦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the Coridan Planets to be admitted to the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而在柯林丹星系中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Coridan system has been claimed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有些种族的代表已经登上了进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by some of the races now aboard our ship as delegates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这些代表因为一些私人原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}races who have strong personal reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,强烈反对柯林丹星加入联邦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for keeping Coridan out of the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而目前进取号所面临的紧要问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The most pressing problem aboard the Enterprise is to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在大会召开前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that open warfare does not break out among the delegates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让登船的各方代表保持理智冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before the conference begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生，我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Ambassador, I understand you had retired
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在这次会议召开以前您已经卸任了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before this conference was called.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我的好奇，但是作为一个医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forgive my curiosity, but, as a doctor, I'm interested in Vulcan physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我对瓦肯人的生理机能很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人在您这个年龄就选择卸任是不太常见的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't it unusual for a Vulcan to retire at your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟您才仅仅102岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After all, you're only 102.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,按照你们的纪年法算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}102.437 precisely, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,确切的说是102.437岁，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Measured in your years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是因为其他的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had other concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大使？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ambassador?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯星的沙瑞克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sarek of Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你会投票同意柯林丹星加入联邦吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you vote to admit Coridan to the Federation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,伽夫大使，投票不是在这儿举行的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The vote will not be taken here, Ambassador Gav.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,您将在巴比伦星的议会大厅里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My government's instructions will be heard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,听到我们政府对此事的表态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the Council Chambers on Babel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我问你，你会赞成还是反对，瓦肯星的沙瑞克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. You. How do you vote, Sarek of Vulcan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒莱特，你为什么非要知道？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why must you know, Tellarite?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在议会里，他的投票是风向标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In council, his vote carries others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要知道他给哪方投票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will know where he stands...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,以及这背后的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒莱特人的争论都是无缘由的，为了争论而争论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tellarites do not argue for reasons. They simply argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不，我问的是你 - 先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. You... - Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克大使先生说的非常对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ambassador Sarek is quite correct when he points out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是巴比伦星的议会大厅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this is not the Council Chamber of Babel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道柯林丹星问题非常有争议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm fully aware that the admission of Coridan is a highly debatable issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你不可能在这儿解决问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you won't solve it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你说的对，非常有逻辑性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are correct, captain. Quite logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My apologies, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生您之前见过伽夫？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you met Gav before, ambassador?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在我上次参加一会的时候我们有过争论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We debated during my last Council session.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大使先生 - 伽夫大使争输了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ambassador. - Ambassador Gav lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我一直怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, I've always suspected
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你其实比你表现出来的更人性化一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you were a little more human than you let on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Sarek,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道对于瓦肯的年轻人有着极其严格的训练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know about the rigorous training of the Vulcan youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他有没有像人类小孩儿一样四处瞎玩儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but tell me, did he ever run and play like the human children, even in secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是偷偷的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，他吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾经养过一只塞拉当宠物，而且非常喜欢它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He did have a pet sehlat he was very fond of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sehlat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一只胖嘟嘟的泰迪熊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's sort of a fat teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一只泰迪熊？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A teddy bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，不好意思，今天对我夫人来说太过劳累了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me, doctor. It has been a rather long day for my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长 - 大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain. - Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一个泰迪熊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这么形容并不准确，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not precisely, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在瓦肯星，这只所谓的泰迪熊是活的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On Vulcan, the teddy bears are alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有着六英寸的獠牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they have six-inch fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥呼叫寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge to Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,感应器收到信号，有不明飞行物正在接近我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensors are registering an unidentified vessel pacing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,马上到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所有值班人员进入黄色警戒，别惊扰了乘客，完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All duty personnel on yellow alert. Don't alarm the passengers. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘小型飞船，舰长，已经尾随我们飞了5分钟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A small ship, captain. It's been there five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,始终在相位炮射程范围之外，处在感应器临界值附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}remaining outside phaser range at extreme limit of sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，身份确认？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Identification, Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,感应器信号显示这是一艘侦查舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensors indicate the size of a scout ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是结构与众不同，情况不寻常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but the configuration is unfamiliar. Most unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对呼叫有回应吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does she answer a hail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过所有的频率，以及宇宙翻译器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've tried all frequencies and hooked in the universal translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 始终没有回应，长官 - 继续用翻译器呼叫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No response, sir. - Maintain translator broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,确认其是否为联邦授权航空器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Check records for authorised ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,星际舰队确认在这个星象中，只有我们是授权船只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starfleet records no authorised vessel in this quadrant except ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想猜猜这艘船是什么人的吗？ - 猜猜？舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Care to guess what she is? - Guess, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要更多的数据来完成预估\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I shall need more data for my estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,契科夫，设定航线准备拦截这艘船舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov, plot a course to intercept that vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我要近距离看看她长什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to see what she looks like close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天晚上让史波克很尴尬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You embarrassed Spock this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个母亲不应该这么做，他是个瓦肯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not even a mother may do that. He is a Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's also human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他是星际舰队的大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a Starfleet officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你反对他参加星际舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you didn't approve of Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是关于我允许他参加舰队的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is not a question of approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,事实是，他已经是星际舰队的成员了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fact exists. He is in Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为了更好的建立威信，他需要被人敬仰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He must command respect if he is to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克，你为他感到骄傲，是不是？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sarek, you're proud of him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在对你儿子感到自豪，就像个人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're showing almost human pride in your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个与骄傲自豪无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It does not require pride
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克应该受到他应得的尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to ask that Spock be given the respect which is his due.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因为他是我儿子，而是因为他是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not as my son, but as Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你能明白吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不完全理解，但是，没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not really. But, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，这么说不合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know. It isn't logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,船舰改变航线，并且正以曲速驶来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vessel changing course. Heading toward us at high warp speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,主相位炮准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready main phasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,相位炮准备就绪，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Phasers armed and ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的速度几乎达到了曲速10\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were travelling at approximately warp 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,返回原来航向，契科夫随时汇报入侵者行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back on original course, Mr. Chekov. Report on intruder's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队收到我们这边的情况汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starfleet acknowledges report on our situation and confirms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,经确认，这个星象中没有联邦授权的飞行器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No authorised Federation vessel in this quadrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,返回原始航线，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back on original heading, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,入侵者也随即改变了他们航线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The intruder changed course immediately after we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 又开始尾随我们飞行了 - 如影随形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's paralleling us again. - Well, we have a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,速度更快，灵活性更高，并且不可识别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Faster, more manoeuvrable, and unidentified.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，全面分析感应器数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, full analysis of sensor readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要知道这个入侵者是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to know who that intruder is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人，我要跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcan, I would speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去这场谈话是无法避免了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It does seem unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对于柯林丹星的提议你会怎么投票？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you vote on the Coridan admission?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生，你看上去等不及会议召开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You seem unwilling to wait for the Council meeting, ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们投赞成票 - 赞成？为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We favour admission. - You favour? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,根据联邦法律，柯林丹星理应得到庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Under Federation law, Coridan can be protected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而其星球的财富也应该用于为他的子民造福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and its wealth administered for the benefit of its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对你们也有好处 瓦肯人对采矿不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's well for you. Vulcan has no mining interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,柯林丹星有着取之不尽的双锂晶体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Coridan has nearly unlimited wealth of dilithium crystals,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是星球本身人口稀少，无力自保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it is underpopulated and unprotected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这就导致了一些非法采矿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This invites illegal mining operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,非法？你这是在指责我们喽？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Illegal. You accuse us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些你们的船舰上面运载着柯林丹星的双锂晶体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some of your ships have been carrying Coridan dilithium crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我们是贼吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You call us thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen. Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们之间的讨论虽然是你们的事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever arguments you have between yourself is your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的职责是维持船舰的平安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My business is running this ship. And as long as I command...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的话就是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...there will be order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然，舰长 - 明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Of course, captain. - Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克，你会为你刚才的诽谤付出代价的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There will be payment for your slander, Sarek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,威胁是不合逻辑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Threats are illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而报复的代价则是高昂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And payment is usually expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,保安部呼叫寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security to Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,乔瑟夫上尉，长官 我在11甲板，A3区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Josephs, sir. I'm on Deck 11, Section A3.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚发现了一个泰勒莱特人，被谋杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just found one of the Tellarites, murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为死者是大使先生本人，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think it's the ambassador himself, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎么死的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How was he killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他的脖子被扭断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His neck was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,职业杀手的作为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,解释一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从伤口的情况以及位置来看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From the nature and the location of the break,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手下手的力度非常精准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd say the killer knew exactly where to apply pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎是立刻毙命的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to snap the neck instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,船舰上有谁有这样的背景？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who aboard would have that knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在瓦肯上，这招叫塔沙亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On Vulcan, the method is called tal-shaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在古代这被认为是一种仁慈的行刑方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was considered a merciful form of execution in ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就在不久前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a short time ago, I broke up an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我打断了伽夫和你父亲的一次争执\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between Gav and your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Indeed, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有意思 - 有意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Interesting. - Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，你有没有意识到这会使你父亲看上去有重大嫌疑？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, do you realise that makes your father the most likely suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人不赞成使用暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcans do not approve of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想说他不会这么做吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you saying he couldn't have done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想说这次没有动机的谋杀不合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm merely saying it would be illogical to kill without reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果他有动机，他能做到吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if he had a reason, could he have done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,假如确实有动机，那么我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there were a reason, my father is quite capable of killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,逻辑上和执行能力是上可以杀人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Logically and efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克夫人，很抱歉打扰您\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Sarek, I'm sorry to disturb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要跟您的先生谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must speak to your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他出去有一会儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's been gone for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,独自冥想是他在退休前就有的习惯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's his habit to meditate in private before retiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，出什么事儿了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's wrong? Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你有事找我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want something of me, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生，泰勒莱特的伽夫被谋杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ambassador, the Tellarite Gav has been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生，他的脖子被扭断了 按照史波克的看法，手法类似于塔沙亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His neck was broken, Mr. Ambassador, by what Spock describes as tal-shaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗？有意思 - 是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Indeed? Interesting. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生，过去的一小时你在什么地方？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ambassador, where were you during the past hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长，你不是要指控他？ - 母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain, you're not accusing him..? - Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从旁证看来他是合乎逻辑的嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only on circumstantial evidence, he is a logical suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常赞成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I quite agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么那一个小时您都在哪儿呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then where were you during the hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我在独自冥想，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In private meditation, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克会告诉你这种冥想是一种非常私隐的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock will tell you that such meditation is a personal experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不能够拿出来讨论，特别是不能跟地球人讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not to be discussed. Especially not with Earthmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个非常说得过去的借口，但是大使先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a very convenient excuse, ambassador, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克，沙瑞克，你怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sarek. Sarek. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就瓦肯人的生理结构而言不好说他到底怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's difficult to say with Vulcan physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我确信这跟他的心血管系统有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I believe it's something to do with his cardiovascular system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你能给他治疗吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know that yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克 - 是的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock. - Yes, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我在入侵船舰舰体上检测到了三钛合金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I get sensor readings of tri-tritanium from the alien ship's hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对于你父亲的事儿，我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，这对于我们这次的任务有不好的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, it could adversely affect our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不担心他吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aren't you worried about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,担心是人类的情感，舰长，我接受所发生的事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Worry is a human emotion, captain. I accept what has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,舰体上检测到的浓度很高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship's hull seems to have a high density level
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,或者它启动了掩体从而反射了传感器信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or is cloaked against sensor probes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行器有人驾驶，但是传感器无法对种族进行解析\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is manned, but sensors cannot make out specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是罗姆兰人的作风\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, the Romulans have nothing like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是联邦或者其他中立星的船舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Certainly not the Federation or the neutral planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,会是克林贡人吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about the Klingons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我认为不像他们中的任何一个 - 那么会是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I think it unlikely it is one of theirs. - Who then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长？ - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我接收到了一段信号，和之前那组来源一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I picked up the last part of a transmission just like that other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我用记录器进行留存，并使用定位器对信号进行锁定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I put the recorder and the directional locator on it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,契科夫，定位器显示来源为方位27，坐标8\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov, directional locator indicates source bearing 27 mark 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正是那艘入侵船舰，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the intruder ship, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，把数据传导给史波克进行解码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Switch recorder to Mr. Spock's station for decode, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,定位器显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The directional locator indicates...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,信号接收端在这艘船舰里的某处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...reception point somewhere within the body of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一个私人接收端？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A personal receiver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,船上有人和那艘飞行器进行联络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody onboard is in contact with that vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是的，舰长，但是我没法完成数据解码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Possibly, captain. But I cannot decode this transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不行？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是已知代码，没有可破译的规律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is in no known code. There is no detectable pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有标准参考值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No standard references apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,从信息自身而言能找到什么线索吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are any conclusions possible from the information?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不能，它不符合我们电脑中的任何一种代码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only negative. It fits none of our computer records.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种外星代码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it is alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会是那个凶手？想在船上玩捉迷藏吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Murder? Somebody out there playing tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，定位感应器改为宽波束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant, you've got your sensor locator on a wide beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,既然已经知道这艘船上有个接收端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've established a receiver onboard this vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那么密切监控船上的每个角落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tighten your field to the interior of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那艘外星飞行器再次开始发信号联络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If that alien vessel starts transmitting again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找到究竟是谁在进取号上跟他们联络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I want to know who onboard the Enterprise is receiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，他怎么样了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,根据检测指标读数，就目前而言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as I can tell from instrument readings,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的头号嫌疑犯心脏瓣膜功能障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}our prime suspect has a malfunction in one of the heart valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这类似于人类的心脏病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's similar to a heart attack in a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.05,0:23:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但就瓦肯星人的生理结构，不做手术我没法给出结论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But with Vulcan physiology, it's impossible to tell without an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克夫人，他之前有过发病史吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Sarek, has he had any previous attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 - 有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,发生过三次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were three others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的医生给我开了苯集塞素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My physician prescribed benjisidrine for the condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉我呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说了也无济于事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was nothing you could have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大使先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ambassador,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候开始发病的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when did you have these attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有两次是在我们离开瓦肯星之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two before we left Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第三次，几小时以前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The third, a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在观测甲板上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was on the Observation Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒莱特人被杀时，我其实是丧失行为能力的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the Tellarite was murdered, I was quite incapacitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没有目击证人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were no witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}None.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，你认为需要对心脏受损实施手术吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, do you propose surgery for the heart defect?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定，即使对人类而言这都是个大手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not sure. It's tough enough on a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而对于瓦肯人，哪怕是寻常的小手术都会变得极其复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On a Vulcan, a ordinary operation is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为瓦肯星人的心脏结构\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because of the construction of the Vulcan heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议进行低温体外循环心脏手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd suggest that a cryogenic open-heart procedure
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.66,0:24:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个合乎逻辑的手术方案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would be the logical approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.12,0:24:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，无可非议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. Unquestionably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，你觉得呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴还有人记得问我的意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad somebody's asking me something around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们提出的这个方案需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, the procedure they're discussing would require
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.26,0:24:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为病人提供大量的血液\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}tremendous amounts of blood for the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.67,0:24:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医生 - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Doctor. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我查了血库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've checked the blood bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.34,0:24:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,船上的瓦肯血液和血浆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There isn't enough Vulcan blood and plasma onboard
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不足以支撑下这样的手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to even begin an operation of this type.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.47,0:24:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 船上还有其他瓦肯星人 - 我的血型是T阴型血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- There are other Vulcans aboard. - My blood type is T-negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.52,0:24:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在瓦肯星上都是稀有血型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somewhat rare, even for a Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.61,0:24:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿，确实不常见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I'd say that's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.23,0:24:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的血型是T阴型血，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My blood is T-negative, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.23,0:24:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对史波克先生的血液做过很多轮的监测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've run a number of blood tests on Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.49,0:24:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是纯瓦肯星血液\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It isn't true Vulcan blood either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.99,0:24:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,里面同时含有人类血液的成分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has human blood elements in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.37,0:24:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,将人类血液成分筛除还是可行的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It should be possible to filter out the human factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.79,0:24:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能提供那么大量的血液，史波克，这会要了你命的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even you couldn't give that much blood, Spock. It would kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.96,0:25:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克夫人，你需要明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Sarek, you must understand, the chances are extremely small
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.51,0:25:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,找到足够T阴型血的几率非常低\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to find a way to produce sufficient T-negative blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.51,0:25:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 的确，我估算出的几率是 - 别说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Indeed. I would estimate the odds... - Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.19,0:25:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过了，史波克，但这是以猎户星人为样本的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see it, Spock, but that was Rigelian.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.78,0:25:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,猎户星人的身体结构和瓦肯人非常接近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rigelian physiology is very similar to Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.20,0:25:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,接近不等于没风险，这毕竟是试验阶段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Similar is not good enough. It's still experimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.24,0:25:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个方法看上去可行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it does look promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.58,0:25:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我们需要的是非常大量的血源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, we would need such great amounts of blood
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.62,0:25:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,即使这个药在瓦肯人身上产生了猎户人的效果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that even if the drug worked on the Vulcans as well as a Rigelian,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.88,0:25:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对此我持保留意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which I am doubtful,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.88,0:25:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克的身体仍然有可能发生危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it would still drain Sarek to a critical level.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.30,0:25:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我考虑到了安全系数很低，但是可接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I consider the safety factor low, but acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.68,0:25:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,况且我从来没给瓦肯星人做过手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plus the fact I've never operated on a Vulcan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.10,0:26:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然接触过解剖标本，也知道各种器官的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I've studied the anatomical types. I know where all the organs are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.52,0:26:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这和实际手术经验差太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's a lot different from actual surgical experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.94,0:26:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以即使我没有失误，那个药物也有可能会要了他命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So if I don't kill him with the operation, the drug probably will.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.78,0:26:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么药，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What drug, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.49,0:26:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫睡着了，什么药？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My husband's asleep. What drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.16,0:26:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一种化学试剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A chemical stimulant to speed up reproduction
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.12,0:26:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以刺激加速血液再生，药物尚在试验阶段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and replacement of blood in the body. It's only experimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.54,0:26:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,药物已经在参宿V星成功完成活体实验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has been used successfully on test subjects on Rigel V.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.26,0:26:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,药物会给脾脏和肝脏带来巨大的负荷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It places a tremendous strain on the spleen and the liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.18,0:26:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就沙瑞克的情形看，这种药物刺激可能会要了他的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In Sarek's condition, the stimulant would kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.90,0:26:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,查佩尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.98,0:26:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,上周我做过一次体检\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I underwent a physical examination last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.48,0:26:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可以麻烦你把相关数据调出来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you pull those records, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.11,0:26:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,已经看过了，史波克，你非常健康\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Already pulled. You're perfectly healthy, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.24,0:27:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你打算干吗？ - 你打算在你身上使用这个药物吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What has that got to..? - You're going to use it on yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.54,0:27:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,加速你自己的造血功能，然后给你父亲输血？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A transfusion from you to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.29,0:27:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唯一的解决方案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would seem the only answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这会使你造成内部器官损伤，这个会是致命的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It could damage you internally. It could kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.30,0:27:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.31,0:27:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能批准这个做法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't sanction it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.10,0:27:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也拒绝这个提议，我不能让你们俩同时冒这么大风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I refuse to permit it. I won't risk both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.44,0:27:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你这个决定就等于是宣判了沙瑞克的死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you automatically condemn Sarek to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.73,0:27:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而你，医生，已经没有比这更符合逻辑的选项了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you, doctor, have no logical alternative, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.74,0:27:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不做手术，沙瑞克就会死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you do not operate, Sarek will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.49,0:27:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在已经有了展开手术的条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You now have the means to perform the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.66,0:27:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而我自愿做一个血液捐助者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am volunteering myself as the blood donor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.34,0:27:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在回到我的工位上，有需要的话就来叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will be at my station until you require me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥呼叫，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.73,0:28:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克 - 我在5号甲板我的舱室附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock here. - I'm on Deck 5 near my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.65,0:29:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我被一个安多利人袭击了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been attacked by an Andorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.82,0:29:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,保安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.12,0:29:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保安部 - 舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Security team. - Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.46,0:29:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长？舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain? Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.61,0:29:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3843.4\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3843.4.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.37,0:29:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,由史波克大副任临时指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First Officer Spock in temporary command.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.87,0:29:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长被参加巴比伦会议的一个代表袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain has been critically wounded
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.87,0:29:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,受了重伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by one of the delegates to the Babel conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.41,0:29:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,全舰警戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship is on Alert Status.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.29,0:29:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,入侵舰仍在尾随\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are still being followed by the intruder vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.80,0:29:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,伤情严重，左肺被刺穿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a bad wound. Punctured left lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.26,0:29:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再低几厘米就会伤到心脏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Centimetre or so lower, it would have gone through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.01,0:29:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去禁闭室审问安多利星的那个嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll be in the brig questioning the Andorian prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.85,0:29:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，K-2指征正在下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, the K-2 factor is dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.98,0:29:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.74,0:30:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲的情况正在恶化，现在已经没的选了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your father is much worse. There's no longer a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须马上为他实施手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to operate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.49,0:30:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你一旦准备好了，我们就马上开始手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can begin as soon as you're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.16,0:30:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行，医生 - 什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No, doctor. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.20,0:30:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,根据星际舰队的规定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My first responsibility is to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.83,0:30:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的首要任务是确保船舰以及乘客的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our passengers' safety is, by Starfleet order, of first importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.88,0:30:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在被一艘未知且不怀好意的船舰尾随\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are being followed by an alien, possibly hostile vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.51,0:30:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能在这样的情况下放弃指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot relinquish command under these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.72,0:30:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以将指挥权移交给史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can turn command over to Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,理由是什么，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On what grounds, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.68,0:30:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,个人意志应绝对服从舰队指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Command requirements do not recognise personal privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.32,0:30:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去禁闭室审讯安多利星人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will be in the brig, interrogating the Andorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.82,0:30:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫泰勒夫，我的低阶侍卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is Thelev, a minor member of my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.41,0:30:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道他工作尽职，其余的并不了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know nothing of him except that he has served adequately.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.20,0:30:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经给他使用了测谎仪和吐真剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He has been subjected to questioning under verifier scan and truth drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.25,0:30:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他并没有说出什么实质的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He reveals nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他对于整体的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I suggest his mind has been so conditioned
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.42,0:30:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所知并不详尽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as part of a preconceived plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.21,0:31:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的族人虽然尚武\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My people are a violent race,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.92,0:31:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们和寇克舰长并没有过节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we had no quarrel with Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.43,0:31:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 泰勒夫显然有 - 这都是你的猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Apparently Thelev did. - Suggest the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.27,0:31:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害舰长对我们有什么好处？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How could it profit us to harm the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.31,0:31:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.94,0:31:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒夫袭击舰长完全不符合逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no logic in Thelev's attack upon the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.36,0:31:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,伽夫遇害也同样毫无逻辑可言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no logic in Gav's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.61,0:31:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该试着不去分析逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps you should forget logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.11,0:31:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而是从动机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Devote yourself to motivations
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.74,0:31:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或者获益方面入手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of passion or gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.37,0:31:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这些才是通常的谋杀动机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those are reasons for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.13,0:31:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.55,0:31:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，你现在必须把指挥权移交给别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, you must turn command over to somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.06,0:31:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲，在我加入舰队的时候曾经宣誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I was commissioned, I took an oath to carry out responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.85,0:31:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我将对我的职位尽忠职守\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which were clearly and exactly specified.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.65,0:32:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,任何有能力的人都能胜任船舰的指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any competent officer can command this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.65,0:32:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只有你能给你父亲输血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only you can give your father the blood transfusions
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.90,0:32:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,来拯救他的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that he needs to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.82,0:32:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在常态下，任何有能力的人都能胜任船舰的指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any competent officer can command this ship under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.74,0:32:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在情况特殊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The circumstances are not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.95,0:32:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,船舰上现在有超过100位联邦星系重要的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're carrying over 100 valuable Federation passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.67,0:32:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,船舰正在被一艘外来战舰尾随，随时可能受到攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're being pursued by an alien ship, we're subject to possible attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.34,0:32:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而船上发生了谋杀以及谋杀未遂的事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There has been murder and attempted murder onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.97,0:32:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能放弃我的职责 - 职责？你的职责应该是挽救你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I cannot dismiss my duties. - Duty? Your duty is to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.43,0:32:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.72,0:32:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在确保船舰安全才是首要职责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But this must take precedence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.35,0:32:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果在不延误时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I could give the transfusion without loss of time or efficiency, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.71,0:32:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,或不影响效率的情况下可以完成输血，我很愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.36,0:32:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克理解我的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sarek understands my reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.94,0:32:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不理解，这太不人性化了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I don't. It's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.49,0:32:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要指责你，但是你也有一部分属于人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, that's not a dirty word. You're human too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.28,0:32:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让你人类的那一半做确定好不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let that part of you come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.16,0:32:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your father's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.25,0:33:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲，你怎么可能在瓦肯生存这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mother, how can you have lived on Vulcan so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.25,0:33:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,与瓦肯人结婚，并生儿育女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}married a Vulcan, raised a son on Vulcan,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.25,0:33:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是却始终不明白对瓦肯人来说什么才是重要的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}without understanding what it means to be a Vulcan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.13,0:33:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我情愿选择我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if this is what it means, I don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.80,0:33:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,选择遵从逻辑并且获益最大的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It means to adopt a philosophy, a way of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.51,0:33:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是瓦肯人的处世之道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which is logical and beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.43,0:33:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能因为一己私欲就漠视这种处世哲学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We cannot disregard that philosophy merely for personal gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,无论这件事有多么重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no matter how important that gain might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.39,0:33:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么能比你父亲的生命更重要的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing is as important as your father's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.19,0:33:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得如果我同意了你的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you imagine what my father would say if I were to agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为父亲一人的性命，从而放弃星舰指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I were to give up command of this vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.61,0:33:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,致上百人性命于危险之中，从而引发星系间的战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}jeopardise hundreds of lives, risk interplanetary war,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.91,0:33:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲会说什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all for the life of one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.29,0:33:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你5岁那年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you were five years old
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.79,0:33:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,满脸伤心气愤的回到家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and came home stiff-lipped, anguished
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.25,0:33:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为其他孩子欺负你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because the other boys tormented you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.92,0:33:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说你不是真正的瓦肯星人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}saying that you weren't really Vulcan...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.88,0:33:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着你，知道在你身体里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I watched you, knowing that inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.93,0:34:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,属于人类的那一半正在哭泣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the human part of you was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.52,0:34:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也跟着掉了眼泪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I cried too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.44,0:34:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个身体里我所赋予的那一半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There must be some part of me in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.28,0:34:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和我是感同身受的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some part that I still can reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.17,0:34:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果做一个真正的瓦肯星人对你来说真这么重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If being Vulcan is more important to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.79,0:34:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就继续守在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then you'll stand there...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.50,0:34:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,高谈阔论那些星际舰队以及瓦肯的原则规矩哲学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...speaking rules and regulations from Starfleet and Vulcan philosophy...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.30,0:34:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然后眼睁睁的看着你父亲死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and let your father die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.97,0:34:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,而我，将用我的余生一直恨你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'll hate you for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.68,0:34:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.48,0:34:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去你父亲那儿吧，求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, go to him now. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.44,0:34:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.46,0:35:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.34,0:35:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在真想按住那个拿锤子的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to get my hands on the guy with the sledgehammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.47,0:35:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,袭击你的那个？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The one who hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.35,0:35:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，在我脑袋里的那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, the one inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.35,0:35:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我昏迷了多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long have l..?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.73,0:35:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能活下来就偷笑了，这是给你个教训\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, let that be a lesson to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.31,0:35:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好还是老老实实的在床上躺着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just lie there and be happy you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.11,0:35:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克怎么样了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How's Sarek?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.94,0:35:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很不好，除非我能做手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not good. If I could only operate...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.28,0:35:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还没做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's stopping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.53,0:35:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为已经万事俱备了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you were all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.16,0:35:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,之前确实是，可你受伤了，史波克接管指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was. When you became injured, Spock assumed command.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.20,0:35:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他会一直坚守岗位，直到你恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's going to stay there till you get back on your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.70,0:35:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,即使这会要了沙瑞克的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even if it costs Sarek his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.12,0:35:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,规章制度什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.21,0:35:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会因为他的尽忠职守而责备他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't damn him for his loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.92,0:35:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也不会让他因此而背负弑父的罪名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For doing his duty. But I'm not going to let him commit patricide.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.34,0:36:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你如果起来伤口又会开始流血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, if you stand, you could start to bleed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.22,0:36:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.73,0:36:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克如果不做手术会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Sarek will die without that operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.23,0:36:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没有史波克输血你无法完成这个手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you can't operate without transfusions from Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.90,0:36:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉史波克我已经没事儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll convince Spock I'm all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.24,0:36:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后命令他到你这儿来，等他从舰桥离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and order him to report here. Soon as he leaves the Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.91,0:36:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把指挥权交给史考特，然后回房间休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll turn command over to Scotty and report to my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.41,0:36:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这也算谨遵医嘱了吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will that fill your prescription?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.47,0:36:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长 - 我现在接手，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain. - I'll take over, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.64,0:36:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在跟麦考伊医生去医务室吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You report to Sickbay with Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.39,0:36:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你确定没问题了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, are you quite all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.43,0:36:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经检查过，他没问题了，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've certified him physically fit, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.10,0:36:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我需要做个手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, since I have an operation to perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.15,0:36:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 咱俩都需要去 - 去吧，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and both of us are required... - Get out, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.62,0:37:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,契科夫，入侵船舰现在什么情况？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov, what's the status of the intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.87,0:37:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有变化，长官，与我们始终保持一定距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No change, sir. Maintaining its distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.08,0:37:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有进一步的通讯联系吗，上尉？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any further transmissions, lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.25,0:37:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}None, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.63,0:37:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让史考特来舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Call Mr. Scott to the Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.30,0:37:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，外星战舰向我方靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, the alien vessel is moving closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.26,0:37:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,收回刚才的指令，我继续指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Belay that order. I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.18,0:37:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我再次收到外来信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I'm picking up the alien signal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.47,0:37:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这次是从进取号内部发出的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's coming from inside the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.02,0:37:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 具体发射源？ - 是禁闭室，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Specific origin? - From the brig, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.94,0:37:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,保安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.23,0:37:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,保安请到禁闭室 立刻搜查嫌疑犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security to the brig. Search the prisoner immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.33,0:37:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,读数，护士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Readings, nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.67,0:38:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克的血液再生指数已经超过200%\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock's blood reproduction rate is up over 200 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.59,0:38:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沙瑞克心跳上升到324\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sarek's heartbeat has risen to 324.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.46,0:38:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,血压90/40 正在下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blood pressure 90/40, dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.05,0:38:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真想知道这代表好还是不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish I knew whether that was good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.18,0:38:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,准备无菌室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Initiate sterile field.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.81,0:38:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.14,0:38:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿？ - 我需要立刻见舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where do you think you're going? - I must see the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.94,0:38:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的病人别想在手术中途四处乱跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My patients don't walk out in the middle of an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.65,0:38:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚意识到，那个外星船舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The alien ship, I just realised,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.53,0:38:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们的动力利用率曲线不同寻常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if their power utilisation curve is not the norm,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.19,0:38:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以利用这个特点来确认他们的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it should be possible to identify them this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.91,0:38:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.33,0:38:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲的命也很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So is your father's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.99,0:39:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.24,0:39:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,保安部，我们不得不打晕那个安多利人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security here. We had to stun the Andorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.99,0:39:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他有某种通讯装置，藏匿在他的触角里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He had some sort of transceiver. It was hidden in his antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.25,0:39:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，外星船舰的航线和速度发生了变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, the alien ship has changed course and speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.71,0:39:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,以曲速8向我们冲过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Moving directly toward us at warp 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.38,0:39:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,把犯人带到舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bring the prisoner to the Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.17,0:39:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,启动防护罩，红色预警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Deflectors on. Red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听我指令，相位炮准备开火 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Phasers stand by to fire on my order. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.26,0:39:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,防护罩启动，相位炮就绪，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shields on, phasers manned and ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 契科夫，接管史波克的扫描器 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Chekov, take over Spock's scanners. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.74,0:39:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,目标，契科夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Target, Mr. Chekov?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.33,0:40:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,它离开了，正在转向，即将驶回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Moving away, turning now. He's coming around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.79,0:40:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,过来就开火，少尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire as he passes, ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.84,0:40:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没打中，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Clean miss, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.05,0:40:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,契科夫，报告他的武器装备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report on his weaponry, Mr. Chekov.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.30,0:40:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,感应器显示只有标准相位炮，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensors record standard phasers, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.63,0:40:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,标准相位炮，很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Standard phasers. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.55,0:40:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们速度很快，但不是不可战胜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have more speed, but they're not giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.64,0:40:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，内部通讯系统阻塞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, the intercoms are jammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.51,0:40:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的大使都在问怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the ambassadors are asking what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.77,0:40:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们自己猜猜，但是什么也别说，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell them to take a good guess, but clear that board, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.27,0:40:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.65,0:40:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它又过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's coming around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.53,0:40:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再这么来一次这俩人我都保不住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One more like that and I'm going to lose both these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.68,0:40:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,武器控制系统已经锁定目标，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire control locked into the computers, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.89,0:40:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,听我命令，发射2号、4号、6号光子鱼雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On my order, fire photon torpedoes two, four, and six.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.56,0:40:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 增大覆盖范围 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Widest possible scatter. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.32,0:41:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.40,0:41:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,都没打中，长官，他们的移动速度远快过我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Full spread missed, sir. They're moving too fast for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.33,0:41:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医生，他停止心跳了 - 心脏起搏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Doctor, his heart's stopped. - Cardiostimulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.88,0:41:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,设备不能运转了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The systems are off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.18,0:41:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把那套旧的便携起搏器拿来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then get me that old portable cardiostimulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.10,0:41:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,通知轮机室，医疗室需要优先恢复供电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Call Engineering and have Sickbay systems put on priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.98,0:41:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.52,0:41:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,4号护盾损坏，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number four shield has buckled, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.53,0:41:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 辅助电源 - 完成切换\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Auxiliary power. - Switching over.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.49,0:41:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,护盾回升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shields firming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.70,0:41:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,4号护盾依然薄弱，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number four is still weak, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.79,0:41:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们再次攻击这个位置，肯定坚持不住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they hit us there again, it'll go altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.27,0:42:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的同伙做的不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your friends out there are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.47,0:42:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是除非完全摧毁这艘星舰，否则他们赢不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll have to destroy this ship to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.31,0:42:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是我们最开始的打算，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That was intended from the beginning, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.40,0:42:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是安多利人，你到底是什么人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not Andorian. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.36,0:42:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，各层甲板都有损毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Damage reports coming in, captain. Every deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.03,0:42:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所有甲板启动损毁控制程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Damage control procedures, all decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.33,0:42:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘船有相位炮，至少武器上我们不相上下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That ship out there has phasers. At least our weapons are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.87,0:42:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,2号护盾损毁，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number two shield is gone, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.29,0:42:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室，这里是舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering. This is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.21,0:42:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,切断左舷除相位炮以外的动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cut power on the port side except for phaser banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.09,0:42:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,听我指令，切断右舷动力，呼叫完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At my signal, cut starboard power. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.43,0:43:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.72,0:43:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己琢磨吧，反正你也活不长了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Find your own answers, captain. You haven't long to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.19,0:43:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个间谍，动过手术变异乔庄成安多利人混上船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a spy, surgically altered to pass as an Andorian,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.07,0:43:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,混进大使团内部，企图用暗杀来制造内讧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}planted in the ambassador's party to use terror and murder to disrupt us,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.45,0:43:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,并且帮助外星船舰进行袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and prepare for this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.36,0:43:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你的臆想，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Speculation, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.28,0:43:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室，切断右舷动力，待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering, cut power on starboard side. Maintain until further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.25,0:43:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,契科夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chekov.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.55,0:43:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.89,0:43:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也臆想一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You speculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.27,0:43:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们开始漂移了，需要我让舰体返回航线吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're starting to drift, sir. Shall I hold her on course?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.85,0:43:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不用，准备好相位炮，契科夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Stand by your phasers, Mr. Chekov.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.65,0:43:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官，相位炮就绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir. Phasers standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.20,0:44:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对方悬停了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's just hovering out there, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.62,0:44:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,正在观察我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looking us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.20,0:44:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它估计觉得我们不行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're dead, as far as he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.00,0:44:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在放诱饵，引它们上钩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're baiting him. You're trying to lure him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.96,0:44:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.22,0:44:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,相隔距离缩短，速度降低接近亚光速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Range decreasing. Speed dropping close to sub-light.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.72,0:44:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,准备开火，契科夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold your fire, Mr. Chekov.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.06,0:44:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,相位炮锁定目标，距离持续缩短\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Phasers locked on target. Range closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.52,0:44:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,75000千米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seventy-five thousand kilometres.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.98,0:44:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.12,0:44:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,打中了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.92,0:44:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,解除战斗部署\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Secure from general quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.13,0:44:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，开启呼叫频率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant, open a hailing frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.51,0:45:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们要投降的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they wish to surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.10,0:45:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不可能投降的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They could not surrender, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.77,0:45:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是死士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had orders to self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.33,0:45:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，把情况汇报给星际舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant, relay to Starfleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.00,0:45:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我们有个在押犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell them we have a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.80,0:45:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.05,0:45:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在押只是暂时的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only temporarily, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.26,0:45:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是名死士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, I had orders to self-destruct too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.14,0:45:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,慢性毒药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Slow poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.64,0:45:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎没有痛苦，也没有解药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite painless, actually, but there is no known antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.44,0:45:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,预计我还能再活10分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I anticipate another ten minutes of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.90,0:45:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,带他去医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take him to Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.11,0:46:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想算错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I seem to have miscalculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.37,0:46:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So did they.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.63,0:46:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,契科夫，接替指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Chekov, take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.09,0:46:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.60,0:46:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直让船舰摇摇晃晃来的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you quite through shaking this ship around?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.01,0:46:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，沙瑞克，他们怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, Sarek. How are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.35,0:46:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你，你给手术的实施增加了巨大的困难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't mind telling you, you sure make it difficult for a surgeon trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.64,0:46:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老骨头！ - 舰长，在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bones! - Captain, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.15,0:46:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了瓦肯星人顽固的毅力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That pig-headed Vulcan stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.24,0:46:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我也不能妙手回春\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I couldn't have pulled them through without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.24,0:46:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,某医生运气不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some doctors have all the luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.83,0:46:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长，我相信你能发现外星 - 我们已经摧毁了那艘船舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain, I believe you'll find the alien... - We damaged their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.95,0:46:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们启动了自毁来避免被俘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They destroyed themselves to avoid capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.96,0:46:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，泰勒夫的尸体会送到你的实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, Thelev's body will be brought to your lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.67,0:47:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你尽快为其做尸检\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want an autopsy performed as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.96,0:47:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你会发现他其实是猎户星人，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you'll find he's an Orion, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.96,0:47:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,猎户星人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orion?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.21,0:47:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有情报指出猎户星走私者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Intelligence reports that Orion smugglers
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.51,0:47:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经洗劫过柯林丹星系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have been raiding the Coridan system.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.22,0:47:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是袭击星际舰队他们又能从中得到什么好处呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what would they gain by an attack on Starfleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.51,0:47:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,内讧和星际大战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mutual suspicion and interplanetary war.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.60,0:47:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿，猎户星是中立的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, of course. With Orion carefully neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.77,0:47:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以向战争双方提供双锂晶体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they'd clean up by supplying dilithium to both sides
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.44,0:47:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,同时继续掠夺柯林丹星的资源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and continue to raid Coridan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.15,0:47:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我觉得不解的是他们的动力源曲线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The thing that confused me was the power utilisation curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.03,0:47:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们比一般我们已知的星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It made them seem more powerful than a starship
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.82,0:47:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,动力更强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or anything known to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.70,0:47:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘星舰是为了执行自杀式袭击的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That ship was constructed for a suicide mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.33,0:47:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们从没有考虑过返航\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since they never intended to return to their home base,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.00,0:47:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才会在袭击的时候使用全部动力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they could use 100 percent power on their attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.38,0:47:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白的是，我之前为什么没能早点儿意识到这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The thing I don't understand is why I didn't think of it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.55,0:47:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你脑子里在想别的事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You might have had something else on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.93,0:47:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这不太可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It hardly seems likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.39,0:47:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿，但是还是谢谢你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. But thank you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.93,0:48:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢，沙瑞克，你是不是也应该谢谢你儿子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you, Sarek. Would you also say thank you to your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.69,0:48:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.94,0:48:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他救了你一命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For saving your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.70,0:48:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克只是在遵从逻辑处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock acted in the only logical manner open to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.37,0:48:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要向逻辑道谢的，阿曼达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One does not thank logic, Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.83,0:48:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,逻辑，逻辑，我受够了讨厌的逻辑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Logic. Logic. I'm sick to death of logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.58,0:48:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道我对你们的那些逻辑怎么想吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want to know how I feel about your logic?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.54,0:48:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她是不是又情绪化了？ - 她经常这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Emotional, isn't she? - She has always been that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.75,0:48:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？那你为什么还娶她？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Indeed? Why did you marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.26,0:48:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候，和她结成连理是非常符合逻辑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the time, it seemed the logical thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.60,0:48:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，没事儿没事儿，我挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones. No, no, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.10,0:48:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是再跟我这个和善的家庭医生较劲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, if you keep arguing with your kindly family doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.94,0:48:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我就让你在床上躺10天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you're going to spend your next ten days right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.98,0:48:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是配合，最多就躺两天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you cooperate, you'll be out in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.94,0:48:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我觉得我可以返回我的岗位了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, I think I'll return to my station now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.99,0:48:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，病床就是你的岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are at your station, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.03,0:48:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生，我觉得你现在乐在其中啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy, I believe you're enjoying all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.45,0:48:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，舰长，我从没见过他这么高兴过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Indeed, captain. I've never seen him look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.37,0:49:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.59,0:49:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈，真不容易，世界终于安静了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, what do you know? I finally got the last word.
